p"><p>Logan applied for a role at OpenAI, on LinkedIn, before they had even=
 launched ChatGPT, and got the job as the first developer relations leader.=
 He=E2=80=99s worked at NASA, Apple, and the Julia Language. Most recently,=
 he left his role at OpenAI to lead product at Google AI Studio. In this ep=
isode we dive into his journey breaking into tech, becoming a thought leade=
r in AI, and his advice for anyone getting into tech.</p><p>Timestamps:</p>=
<ul><li><p>1:55: what leaving OpenAI was like</p></li><li><p>4:30: how appl=
ying cold on LinkedIn led to a role at OpenAI</p></li><li><p>10:20: what de=
veloper advocacy looked like early on at OpenAI</p></li><li><p>13:25: figur=
ing out the next play after OpenAI and joining Google</p></li><li><p>20:25:=
 advice for folks early in their career</p></li></ul><p><strong><span>Thank=
 you to our sponsor Notion. Make sure to sign up for Notion using this link=
